    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057280/extras/391eacacfa1c44ef0bf799dc558f8c13.avif?t=1769617684\" width=1560 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057280/extras/5ff36076e4b60e37c04b5626ae0ed3c1.poster.avif?t=1769617684\" width=780 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057280/extras/5ff36076e4b60e37c04b5626ae0ed3c1.webm?t=1769617684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057280/extras/5ff36076e4b60e37c04b5626ae0ed3c1.mp4?t=1769617684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《灌木小子》</strong>是一款轻松休闲的3D平台收集类游戏，其灵感来源于复古平台游戏及其独特的魅力。扮演灌木小子与背包小子这对全新的搭档，踏上一段异想天开的冒险，从邪恶巫师手中夺回所有被盗的洗澡鸭，挫败他的邪恶阴谋！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>来看看我们目前正在进行的 Kickstarter 项目：</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057280/extras/170b52c87b9cd8d83fb2c177ff24c78b.avif?t=1769617684\" width=1560 height=468 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">一对全新的搞怪搭档！<strong>灌木小子与背包小子！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057280/extras/e58ab405708a3ed009adcaded65af0ec.avif?t=1769617684\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057280/extras_big/e58ab405708a3ed009adcaded65af0ec.webp?t=1769617684 width=1560 height=1314 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057280/extras/0b9d3805c25902d475a08db8db8a84ac.avif?t=1769617684\" width=1560 height=473 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057280/extras/8ed1014ff98917ab087f90357264c62c.poster.avif?t=1769617684\" width=780 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057280/extras/8ed1014ff98917ab087f90357264c62c.webm?t=1769617684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057280/extras/8ed1014ff98917ab087f90357264c62c.mp4?t=1769617684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>与众多超酷的角色交谈！</strong>他们有的会给你带来有用的信息，有的则会向你寻求帮助！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057280/extras/0e03509acd57bba1e9e639c750fa77a1.avif?t=1769617684\" width=1560 height=473 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057280/extras/a9e38c963e8f290ee1b689f4f217afcd.poster.avif?t=1769617684\" width=780 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057280/extras/a9e38c963e8f290ee1b689f4f217afcd.webm?t=1769617684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057280/extras/a9e38c963e8f290ee1b689f4f217afcd.mp4?t=1769617684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>探索五彩斑斓的迷人世界！</strong>你能找出所有隐藏的秘密吗！？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p cl